    "text": "Symptom: attackers killed their prey and then rammed the fresh corpse \u2014 the kill-cone striker self-eliminated 42% of the time. Lengthening the kill cone alone cut that but collapsed matches into mutual-annihilation draws. Adding a stand-off engagement distance (strike from cone reach, don't ram) and a modest reach increase together dropped self-elimination to 20% while keeping 67% of matches decisive. We measured each lever instead of guessing."
